<i>verb</i>: 응징하다 [응ː징하다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>응징하다 [응ː징하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. punish; chastise</dd><br>
<dd>잘못을 깨닫고 뉘우치도록 벌을 주어 나무라다.</dd><br>
<dd>To punish and rebuke someone so that he/she realizes and regrets his/her wrongdoing.</dd><br>
<dd>2. subjugate</dd><br>
<dd>적국을 무력으로 쳐서 굴복하게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To attack the enemy country and make it succumb by using armed force.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>